categories: Category:Jedi Masters of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: Tenbrai was a female Human Jedi Master who served the Jedi Order on the Galactic Republic's capital of Coruscant during the Cold War between the Sith Empire and the Republic. A dark-skinned Human, Tenbrai wore armored robes that were brown and tan in color, and she wielded two lightsabers in combat.
Tenbrai first appeared in Game Update 1.2 of Star Wars: The Old Republic, a video game released by BioWare and LucasArts in 2011, as the Legacy vendor for the Jedi Knight class.
